Name:                indexed
Version:             0.1.3
Synopsis:            Haskell98 indexed functors, monads, comonads
Description:         Haskell98 indexed functors, monads, comonads
License:             BSD3
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Edward A. Kmett
Maintainer:          Reiner Pope <reiner.pope@gmail.com>
Copyright:           
